 Instructions: (Non-Root/Offline)

- Install APK
- Copy 'com.gameloft.android.ANMP.GloftM4HM' folder to 'sdcard/Android/obb/'
(Needs new main obb 1100 to run the game)
- Launch the Game
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The #1 Action FPS game is back on smartphone with a new chapter to push the boundaries of mobile gaming even further. In the wake of nuclear warfare, the only chance to avoid global devastation is in the hands of the few elite soldiers who must track down and rescue the worldÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s leaders from a frighteningly familiar terrorist group.

DIVE INTO THE MOST MEMORABLE ACTION SHOOTER EVER

